        {
            "title": "恒生私有化對價支票料於下周三或之前寄發",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)與恒生銀行(00011)再就恒生私有化計畫發公告，表示計畫所有條件均已達成，計畫已於今日變具約束力且生效。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：恒生銀行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_00011.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：恒生銀行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_00011.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：恒生銀行官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生私有化計畫的對價支票，預期於下周三(2月4日)或之前寄發；以電子銀行轉賬方式支付的對價，預期同在下周三或之前作出。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據港交所(00388)批准，恒生股份在港上市地位，將於明天下午4時正被撤銷。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15613221-%e6%81%92%e7%94%9f%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96%e5%b0%8d%e5%83%b9%e6%94%af%e7%a5%a8%e6%96%99%e6%96%bc%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%89%e6%88%96%e4%b9%8b%e5%89%8d%e5%af%84%e7%99%bc",
